<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: MY TRAITOR'S HEART A SOUTH AFRICAN EXILE RETURNS TO FACE HIS 
COUNTRY, HIS TRIBE AND HIS CONSCIENCE BY RIAN MALAN (A MORGAN ENTREKIN 
BOOK/ATLANTIC MONTHLY: $19.95; 372 PP.) 
