<HEADLINE>
<P>
BOOKSELLERS AND WRITERS AGAINST HOMELESSNESS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Southern California Booksellers Assn., PEN Center U.S.A. West, The National 
Book Foundation and The Homeless Writers Coalition, in conjunction with the 
publication of "Louder Than Words" (Vintage Books) present a series of events 
spotlighting homelessness in our society. 
</P>
