TODAY 
</P>
<P>
Santa Monica. Musicians D. J. Bonebrake (X), Steve Wynn (Dream Syndicate), Tom 
Boyd (Artists Against Homelessness); authors Steve Erickson ("Leap Year"), 
Judith Freeman ("Chinchilla Farm"), Anthony Hernandez (photographer, 
"Landscapes of the Homeless"), Jackie Joseph (LADIES), Carolyn See ("Louder 
Than Words"). At My Place, 2-3:30 p.m., 1026 Wilshire Blvd., 1:30 p.m., $3; 
food bins available for donations. Information: (213)-451-8596. 
</P>
