(Homeless Writers Coalition), Jeanne Cooper (Venice Voices) and Rosanna DeSoto 
(actress, "Family Business"), Midnight Special Bookstore, 7:30 p.m., 1350 3rd 
St. Promenade, 7:30 p.m., $5., all proceeds to benefit homeless writers; food 
