NEXT SUNDAY 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills. Artists Against Homelessness: A fund raiser for the Cultural 
Center for the Homeless, including readers from The Homeless Writers Coalition 
and a screening of Rob Stone's "Sidewalk Motel," Fine Arts Theatre, 8556 
Wilshire Blvd., 12:30 p.m., admission: one can of food. Information: (213) 
393-2933. 
</P>
<P>
* Bins also will be available for food and clothing at the following locations, 
today through Feb. 17: 
</P>
<P>
Santa Monica. Change of Hobbit Books, 1433 2nd St. 
</P>
<P>
West Hollywood. Book Soup, 8818 Sunset Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
Pasadena. Page One Books, 966 N. Lake, Pasadena. 
</P>
<P>
Donations of food will benefit the Westside Food Bank, 604B Colorado Ave., 
Santa Monica. Information: (213) 314-1150. 
