because the club is dry. LAWRENCE K. HO / L.A. Times; Photo, T.S.O.L. performs 
at West Hollywood's Roxy, which is probably the most popular stage in Los 
Angeles. TORU KAWANA / L.A. Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
