<TEXT>
<P>
I enjoyed John G. Zawadzinski's article of Jan. 28 on Mieczyslaw Horszowski 
(and attended his Jan. 31 recital at the Dorothy Chandler Pavilion). However, 
Mr. Zawadzinski incorrectly identifies the Juilliard School as the Juilliard 
School of Music. 
</P>
<P>
The school dropped "of Music" from the name when drama and dance divisions were 
added and the school moved to Lincoln Center. 
