victory over UCLA. ; Photo, (Southland Edition) UCLA's Trevor Wilson applies an 
ice pack after being elbowed by Arizona's 7-foot Ed Stokes during first half. 
Arizona won, 83-74. ROB SCHUMACHER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
