</CORRECTION-DATE>
<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Council race -- A story about the cost of the 1989 Montebello City Council 
election (Times, Feb. 11) incorrectly listed Quiet Cannon Montebello Inc. as a 
defendant in a libel suit filed by Montebello City Councilman William Molinari. 
The same story referred to David Perrin as the organizer of a political action 
committee that opposed Molinari during the 1987 council election. Campaign 
disclosure statements do not list Perrin as either an organizer or member of 
the political action committee. The statements show only that Perrin 
contributed $950 to the committee. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
