<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In an item in last week's Outtakes, Richard Gere was quoted as saying that he 
would like to get a film project going about the life of Buddha and portray the 
religious leader in that movie. 
</P>
<P>
Gere, through his publicist, has denied speaking with the author of the item 
and says that he would never consider casting himself in such a role, which he 
feels should be played by an Asian. Gere, in fact, was never interviewed. 
</P>
</TEXT>
