COUNTY; COASTAL AREAS -- ORANGE COUNTY; WATER POLLUTION -- ORANGE COUNTY; OCEAN 
POLLUTION; BEACHES; HUNTINGTON BEACH (CA) -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; MAYORS; NEWS 
CONFERENCES; MAYS, THOMAS J 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
